  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This open-label, randomized, parallel-group clinical study is designed to compare the
      efficacy and safety of the topical antibiotic, sisomicin cream, with that of another topical
      antibiotic cream, nadifloxacin cream, in the treatment of Indian patients with primary
      pyodermas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
